title: Ebro In The Morning - Robots, Jeopardy + Baby Girl: Better Known as Aaliyah
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/20. Guest Kathy Iandoli comes on the program to talk about her book "Baby Girl: Better Known as Aaliyah."

Ebro talks robots and Jeopardy, Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (10), and you find out who played themselves.
